Usage

smooth_model(x, u_init, v_init, w, index, lambda, epsilon, maxiter)

Arguments

x

sparse matrix; assay matrix

u_init

matrix; u initialization matrix

v_init

matrix; v initialization matrix

w

matrix; distance matrix. If null, computed to specification with k nearest neighbors.

index

w indicies.

lambda

positive numeric; penalization parameter.

epsilon

positive numeric; convergence criterion.

maxiter

positive integer; maximum desired iterations

Value

SummarizedExperiment object with u, v and cluster labels.
